            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>亞培(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ABT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ABT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ABT-US</a>)截至台北時間17日21:33股價下跌6.68美元，報125.06美元，跌幅5.07%，成交量1,061,918（股），盤中最高價126.86美元、最低價124.94美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.28%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.08%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.06%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-0.35%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>亞培(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ABT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ABT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ABT-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-1.11%</li> <li>近 1 月：-1.69%</li> <li>近 3 月：+1.57%</li> <li>近 6 月：+15.65%</li> <li>今年以來：+16.47%</li></ul></section></main>",
